      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, offering a rare opportunity to own a car that presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, consistent shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is an exceptional example suited for a collector or anyone seeking a vehicle in impeccable, like-new condition.",
