    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, super reliable, and honestly still looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
