    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with crisp turn-in and minimal body roll, while the braking system provides consistent bite with no signs of fade. This is a mechanically sound driver's car that exemplifies the peak of BMW's naturally aspirated engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
