    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a stunning 2019 Performance Sedan in Mythos Black Metallic. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and exhilarating daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though it shows a few honest signs of the road, including minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger alloy wheel. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium black leather and brushed aluminum. The seats remain supple with minimal bolster wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the virtual cockpit to the premium surround sound\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is top-tier. I have strictly followed the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule, with the most recent oil service and brake inspection completed just last month. It shifts smoothly, pulls hard, and handles with precision. It comes with a clean title, two keys, and a thick folder of maintenance records. If you are looking for a car that balances high-end performance with everyday usability and has been cared for by an enthusiast, this is the one.",
